greyfox.rxnetwork.internal.net

Class RxNetworkInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • greyfox.rxnetwork.internal.net.RxNetworkInfo

  • public class RxNetworkInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper class for NetworkInfo.

    For pre-Lollipop (API < 21) this class is simple one-to-one wrapper of NetworkInfo.

    Starting from Lollipop (API >= 21) it provides additional NetworkCapabilities information to the class.
